race.comment: HOTCH POTCH (1) progressed nicely last time out to finish a narrow second over 1800m at Clare after being in the firing line on the turn. Best figures measure up. Sure to run well. PRINCESS ON PALM (4) is backing up just two days after she was strongly fancied and finished third over this trip. Strong run last time and is worth following up. VEE ROD (8) turned in a fine effort to score well over this track and distance last start in a much improved run. Likely to be there at the finish again. ROKABYE WARRIOR (2) finished second at Lock two runs back but didn't measure up last time. Better placed here and is one to keep safe in the numbers.
